		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>I don't know if you noticed, but they avoided using any files at all with a dimension greater than 256 pixels. The reason for this is that there are still people out there who use graphic cards that don't support textures over 256 pixels in size.<br />
<br />
They were just trying to avoid breaking the game for some of their customers.</div>
